def calculateAge(birthDate):
    today = datetime.date.today()
    year = int(birthDate.strftime("%Y"))
    month = int(birthDate.strftime("%m"))
    day = int(birthDate.strftime("%d"))
    age = today.year - year - ((today.month, today.day) < (month, day)) 
    return age
